=== Birth ===
Generally considered to be born in 1739.
* There is no document with Peter's birth year, and none with even a decade bracket at any point in time, aside from being "45 and above" in the 1810 and 1820 censuses.
* Peter's father Hans Jacob was married in 1734 and died in 1752, so it is likely that Peter was under 18 at Hans Jacob's death.  The difficulties of migration and a possible requirement for an indentured period may have further delayed the arrival of Jacob's children.
* On 19 May 1762:  "Peter, Elizabeth, Hannah, Barbara, Catharine, Orphans of Jacob Rodcap, to be bound to Geo. Hollowback.  Moses Maiden to be bound."<ref>Chronicles of the Scotch-Irish settlement in Virginia, Lyman Chalkley, [Virginia] : M.S. Lockwood, 1912, Vol 1 Page 97, https://www.familysearch.org/library/books/viewer/202922/?offset=0#page=97&viewer=picture&o=info&n=0&q=</ref>.  If Peter is not of age in 1762, as the guardian bond suggests, then his birth year could be several years later than what is generally considered to be true.  Peter's brother John George is absent from the list, suggesting that Peter is the younger brother.

